{
  "text": "How about the seven bodily energy centers? Are they related to archetypes in some way? I am Ra. The same may be said of these. It is informative to view the relationships but stifling to insist upon the limitations of congruency. Recall at all times, if you would use this term, that the archetypes are a portion of the resources of the mind complex.",
